from collections import defaultdict, deque

graph = defaultdict(set)
n, k = map(int, input().split())
for i in range(k):
    a, b = map(int, input().split())
    graph[b].add(a)

visited = set()
component = []
q = deque()
q.append(1)
visited.add(1)
while q:
    v = q.popleft()
    component.append(v)
    for neighbor in graph[v]:
        if neighbor not in visited:
            visited.add(neighbor)
            q.append(neighbor)

print(*sorted(visited))
